<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.8">
<l>celva nāraṇa ṉeṉṟacol kēṭṭalu</l>
<l>malkuṅ kaṇpaṉi nāṭuvaṉ māyamē</l>
<l>yallu naṉpaka lumiṭai vīṭiṉṟi</l>
<l>nalki yeṉṉai viṭā ṉampi nampiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As soon as I hear the word that say “o lord, Nārāyaṇa”,</l>
<l>tears well up in [my] eyes. I ponder the wonder.</l>
<l>By night and by day without release</l>
<l>he grants [his presence and] does not let me go, Nampi, Nampi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
